00:00:09.121 --> 00:00:12.161
what some of the members of the PC caucus were doing, uh,

00:00:12.162 --> 00:00:14.181
during this last question period.

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:17.280
Before I get into that, it's important to know that actually

00:00:17.281 --> 00:00:21.321
