00:00:34.082 --> 00:00:36.261
Today's a really important day.

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:39.280
Like it's a historical moment right now,

00:00:39.281 --> 00:00:42.941
the start of this fourth phase of the landfill search.

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:46.620
And so during question period,

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:49.960
the cabinet ministers that were asked questions

00:00:49.961 --> 00:00:53.021
took the opportunity to remind the PC caucus

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:56.720
what they did in the last provincial election

00:00:56.721 --> 00:00:58.441
in the 2023 election.

00:00:58.442 --> 00:01:03.941
And folks will remember it was a very hateful and divisive campaign.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.140
But they also centered their campaign

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:09.140
over the question of searching the landfill.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:14.840
They centered the campaign on the murders of indigenous women

00:01:14.841 --> 00:01:16.421
by a serial killer,

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:20.860
