00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:43.240
has never apologized for What their election,

00:01:43.241 --> 00:01:46.861
with their party, with their people did during that campaign.

00:01:47.160 --> 00:01:51.080
And so during QP today, our members that got up

00:01:51.081 --> 00:01:54.181
took the opportunity to remind them of what they did.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:57.640
And while our folks were answering those questions,

00:01:57.641 --> 00:01:59.601
I want to share with you what some of them were doing.

